<%= render 'shared/legal_nav' %>

<!-- Main Content -->
<main class="pt-24 pb-16 bg-[#f9f9f9] min-h-screen">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="text-center mb-12">
      <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl text-black mb-4">CREATOR TERMS</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-600">Terms of Use for Flikk Creators</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Earnings Highlight -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-100 via-pink-100 to-orange-100 rounded-3xl p-6 md:p-8 mb-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 text-center">
        <div>
          <div class="font-display text-4xl text-black">80%</div>
          <div class="text-gray-700">You Keep</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-display text-4xl text-black">20%</div>
          <div class="text-gray-700">Platform Fee</div>
        </div>
        <div>
          <div class="font-display text-4xl text-black">₹0</div>
          <div class="text-gray-700">Joining Fee</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Content -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-lg p-6 md:p-10 space-y-8">
      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">1. BECOMING A CREATOR</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          By applying to become a Flikk creator, you agree to these Creator Terms in addition to our general Terms of Service. 
          To be eligible as a creator:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4 mt-4">
          <li>You must have at least 10,000 followers across your social media platforms</li>
          <li>You must be at least 18 years old</li>
          <li>You must complete age and identity verification</li>
          <li>You must agree to our content guidelines (no nudity allowed)</li>
          <li>You must provide accurate information about yourself</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">2. CREATOR OBLIGATIONS</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">As a Flikk creator, you commit to:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4 mt-4">
          <li><strong>Guaranteed Responses:</strong> Respond to paid fan messages within 24-48 hours</li>
          <li><strong>Quality Content:</strong> Provide valuable, original content to your subscribers</li>
          <li><strong>Authenticity:</strong> Be genuine and authentic in your interactions</li>
          <li><strong>Brand Safety:</strong> Maintain a brand-safe, family-friendly profile (no nudity)</li>
          <li><strong>Regular Engagement:</strong> Actively engage with your fan community</li>
          <li><strong>Transparency:</strong> Be clear about what fans can expect from their subscription</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">3. EARNINGS AND PAYMENTS</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">How you earn on Flikk:</p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4 mt-4">
          <li><strong>Subscriptions:</strong> Set your own monthly subscription price</li>
          <li><strong>Tips:</strong> Receive tips from fans who want to show extra support</li>
          <li><strong>Paid DMs:</strong> Charge for direct message access</li>
          <li><strong>Unlocked Content:</strong> Offer exclusive content for additional purchase</li>
          <li><strong>Livestreams:</strong> Earn during live sessions through tips</li>
        </ul>
        <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-xl p-4 mt-4">
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            <strong>Revenue Split:</strong> You keep 80% of all earnings. Flikk retains 20% to maintain the platform, 
            provide support, and continue improving features.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">4. PAYMENT SCHEDULE</h2>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4">
          <li>Payments are processed monthly</li>
          <li>Minimum payout threshold: ₹500</li>
          <li>Payments are made via bank transfer or UPI</li>
          <li>You are responsible for any applicable taxes on your earnings</li>
          <li>Earnings are tracked in real-time through your Creator Dashboard</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">5. CONTENT OWNERSHIP</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          You retain full ownership of all content you create and share on Flikk. By posting content, you grant Flikk 
          a non-exclusive license to display your content within the platform to your subscribers.
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4 mt-4">
          <li>You are responsible for ensuring you have rights to all content you share</li>
          <li>You must not share copyrighted material without permission</li>
          <li>You can remove your content at any time</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">6. CREATOR SUCCESS SUPPORT</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          As a Flikk creator, you get access to:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4 mt-4">
          <li>Dedicated Creator Success team for support</li>
          <li>Marketing coaching to grow your audience</li>
          <li>Analytics and insights to track your growth</li>
          <li>Priority customer support</li>
          <li>Access to exclusive creator events and experiences</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">7. ACCOUNT TERMINATION</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          Your creator account may be terminated if you:
        </p>
        <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-gray-700 space-y-2 ml-4 mt-4">
          <li>Violate content guidelines (especially the no-nudity policy)</li>
          <li>Fail to respond to fan messages consistently</li>
          <li>Engage in fraudulent activities</li>
          <li>Provide false information during verification</li>
          <li>Repeatedly violate Terms of Service</li>
        </ul>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mt-4">
          You may also choose to close your creator account at any time. Outstanding earnings will be paid out 
          according to the normal payment schedule.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="font-display text-2xl text-black mb-4">8. CONTACT</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          For creator-specific questions or support:
        </p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 mt-4">
          <strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:creators@flikk.co.in" class="text-pink-500 hover:underline">creators@flikk.co.in</a>
        </p>
      </section>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="text-center mt-8">
      <%= link_to creator_registration_path, class: "btn-primary px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold inline-flex items-center space-x-2" do %>
        <span>Apply to Become a Creator</span>
        <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14 5l7 7m0 0l-7 7m7-7H3"></path>
        </svg>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <!-- Back Link -->
    <div class="text-center mt-4">
      <%= link_to root_path, class: "inline-flex items-center space-x-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-black transition-colors" do %>
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M10 19l-7-7m0 0l7-7m-7 7h18"/>
        </svg>
        <span>Back to Home</span>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</main>

<%= render 'shared/legal_footer' %>

